            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "We really loved the school and have been happy for a few years. They started off really well but for the past couple of months things have been going downhill.  Recently, the school has been challenging to work with. We have struggled with getting responses to security concerns, emails go unanswered, there is a general arrogance in the senior staff. In addition, the infrastructure is under construction which is something we have been adjusting with but the fact that the school is lax about security and unresponsive is serious enough for us to consider changing the school. Their sports especially are way below the mark. The management is very amateur and can’t believe this is a brand like Bvrtse.",
